OL,3,CCovert police officers to be used to
OL,4,Ccatch sexual predators as offences soar
OL,6,FCovert police officers are going to be
OL,7,Fdeployed in Bristol in a bid to tackle
OL,8,Fthe rising number of cases of rape and
OL,9,Fsexual offences.
OL,11,FThe number of recorded rapes in the
OL,12,Fcity rose by almost a quarter last
OL,13,Fyear, according to the latest police
OL,14,Ffigures.
OL,16,FSuperintendent Mark Runacres, the
OL,17,Fcity's police commander, was called to
OL,18,FBristol City Council's public health
OL,19,Fpolicy committee to give an update on
OL,20,FFriday 17 January.
