OL,3,CCovert police officers to be used to
OL,4,Ccatch sexual predators as offences soar
OL,6,F"In the coming months we'll be
OL,7,Flaunching a proactive operation in the
OL,8,Fcity centre," he told councillors.
OL,10,F"We'll be deploying officers, overtly
OL,11,Fand covertly, to try and identify
OL,12,Fpredatory offenders who are exhibiting
OL,13,Fbehaviours of concern, and then being
OL,14,Fable to intervene at an early point to
OL,15,Fdeal with them accordingly", Supt
OL,16,FRunacres added.
OL,18,FLast year, the number of rapes of
OL,19,Fwomen aged 16 and over rose by 23 per
OL,20,Fcent, from 423 in the previous
OL,21,Frecorded year to 522.
