OL,6,FThe total number of sexual offences
OL,7,Fhas also increased, rising from 1,536
OL,8,Fto 1,644 last year.
OL,10,FCouncillors believe a change of
OL,11,Fculture is needed to help address rise
OL,12,Fin sexual crimes. Schools in Bristol
OL,13,Fhave already been tasked with
OL,14,Fimproving their culture and preventing
OL,15,Fteenagers from believing that violence
OL,16,Fagainst women is acceptable.
OL,18,FLabour Councillor Emily Clarke said:
OL,19,F"This week in my ward (Bedminster), I
OL,20,Fhad a really quite shocking example.
