OL,6,F"At one of the secondary schools there
OL,7,Fwas graffiti in the tunnels on the way
OL,8,Fto that school talking about freeing
OL,9,Fsomebody who's been accused of rape
OL,10,Fand celebrating that person. At the
OL,11,Fmoment it feels like we're going in
OL,12,Fthe wrong direction."
OL,14,FResponding to this, the council said
OL,15,Fit is carrying out work in more than
OL,16,Fhalf the schools in Bristol around
OL,17,Fdomestic abuse, sexual violence and
OL,18,Fhealthy relationships. Those that
OL,19,Fchange their culture, improve the
OL,20,Fcurriculum and invest in training can
OL,21,Freceive the Bristol Ideal Award.
