OL,6,FCarol Slater, head of the council's
OL,7,Fpublic health service, said: "In
OL,8,Fschools we have the Ideal programme,
OL,9,Fwhich is all about relationships and
OL,10,Fgender.
OL,12,F"We're trying to engage more schools
OL,13,Fin that programme. We've currently got
OL,14,Fabout 60 per cent of schools signed
OL,15,Fup, but we need to get more signed up
OL,16,Ftoo."
